Funny isn't it!  Nobody is better than anyone else!  Little silver wings don't make you bullet proof.  Color of your uniform don't make your chances any better.  Smart guys make mistakes just like the dumbasses.  Officers bleed to death just like PFCs. People on and off the battlefield pay horrific prices.  Envy is always the best form of flattery!  A few always seem to know the most.  My Daddy can't always beat up your Daddy!   Zippos don't always light.  The check isn't necessarily in the mail.  And..all experts aren't really experts.<br>
If you don't have any friends... you probably need to take a bath...if that don't work, you've got some serious problems.Want to know if you are doing okay!  Look at your kids...the answer is there!<br>
Clearing a mine field same same as making a 13 year old daughter clean her room...you have to be gentle!<br>
Thanks Tom, John, SW...Welcome Home, Jed!<br><br>
